Excited to share my new sample pack "Elemental" with you! Out now on Splice Sounds.

"Since breaking onto the scene with his Seven Lions remix for OWSLA, Au5 has been shattering expectations for dance music producers by dipping into every genre under the sun.

His effortless fusion of epic trance melodies, morphing dubstep basslines and crisp electro percussion can now be yours in this exclusive sample pack. Explore the true meaning of bass music innovation with handcrafted synth loops, drum fills, bass growls, FX and more."
-Splice
